{{Top|leg}}
A '''Lungworm''' was a biotechnological creature [[Shaper caste|shaped]] by the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] to supply air to to the [[gnullith]] worn with a [[Ooglith cloaker|vacuum ooglith]], their equivalent of a spacesuit. Worn coiled on the wearer's back, it reached round over the shoulder to connect its mouth to the gnullith, and it could supply air for up to two hours&mdash;at which point, having run out of air itself, it would expire.

